#careforsg

1.4M views

Post a video and TikTok donates to Community Chest. TikTok Singapore will donate a specified amount, depending on the level of challenge participation: X = hashtag creations 50k ≤ X < 100k: $50,000 in total 100k ≤ X < 200k: $100,000 in total X ≥ 200k : $200,000 in total (max) Donation will be made in SGD in Singapore. For more information: https://bit.ly/2AotCDc [How to Support] Go to the 'Shooting Page' to take a video and use the "CareForSG” sticker You can do the sign language for “Care” and smile to show you #CareForSG! TikTok will donate $1 to The Invictus Fund for every video posted with the filter! Every TikTok account can post up to five (5) videos. Time to spread some cheer and bring hope to over 80 charities as they overcome the challenges with COVID-19 and continue to serve the vulnerable. Together, we can bring a smile to the faces of the vulnerable in Singapore! Globally, TikTok is committed to donating up to USD 10 million for COVID-19 support.
